ygData.messageBody:
as a Darkelf Necro I made I was L1 and killed nothing really but spiders and
I was not KOS in Freeport. . .
Dubios, but not KOS . . . tok boat over to BB, jumped off boat once in bb
zone swam to shore on left and ran to GF dodgeing Dwarves. Then got a
bind in GF and was all set.



If you want a
> place close by to sell... find the way to the necro guild in freeport.
(in
> east freeport... don't go to north freeport until you have hunted orcs
intil
> you were sick of it... then hunted more orcs untill your dog, cat, kids,
> wife, mom, dad, and the rest of your neghborhood are sick of you hunting
> orcs... than maybee you can get into north freeport without being killed.)
> While the prices are not as good as Neriak... it is a shorter trip. You
will
> still have to periodically go back to Neriak to bank. (the bank in
freeport
> is in North Freeport...)
>
> Sonoroud, 19th Level Dark Elf Necromancer
